longBusinessSummary: King Wan Corporation Limited, an investment holding company, provides mechanical and electrical engineering services for the building and construction industry in Singapore. It operates through Plumbing and Sanitary, Electrical & ACMV, and Toilet Rental segments. The Plumbing and Sanitary segment designs and installs water distribution systems and pipe network for sewage and waste water drainage. The Electrical & ACMV segment engages in designing and installation of electricity distribution systems, fire protection, alarm systems, communications, and security systems, as well as air-conditioning and mechanical ventilation systems. Toilet Rental segment rents and operates mobile lavatories and other facilities. In addition, it engages in trading of eco-friendly products. The company was founded in 1977 and is headquartered in Singapore.
